event_name: Prime Timers (Senior Adults): Aurora day trip

event.description: We will spend the day in the National Historic District of Aurora. This small town has distinctive architecture, antiques and vintage shops, specialty retail and eateries as well as a class-act museum. We will meet at the church at 9am and carpool to Aurora. Lunch will be at the White Rabbit Bakery at 12:30. Contact Elaine Thornlimb / elainethornlimb@gmail.com / (971) 275-2136
